---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const lastUpdated = '29 April 2026';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | St. Claret College of Nursing" activeNav="">

  <section class="relative py-24 bg-navy overflow-hidden">
    <div class="relative max-w-container mx-auto px-8 text-center flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
      <span class="font-work-sans font-semibold text-gold text-sm uppercase tracking-[2.8px]">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-newsreader italic text-5xl md:text-6xl text-white leading-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[#FBF6E3] text-base">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-light-bg px-8 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12 prose prose-slate prose-headings:font-newsreader prose-headings:italic prose-headings:text-navy prose-h2:text-3xl prose-h2:mt-10 prose-h2:mb-4 prose-p:text-text-secondary prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-li:text-text-secondary prose-a:text-navy prose-strong:text-navy max-w-none">

      <p>
        St. Claret College of Nursing ("we", "us", "our") respects your privacy. This policy explains
        what information we collect when you visit <strong>stclaretcollegeofnursing.com</strong> or contact our
        admissions office, how we use it, and the choices you have.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information that you voluntarily provide to us, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Inquiry details</strong> — your name, phone number, email address, course of interest, and any message you submit through our admissions form or popup.</li>
        <li><strong>Communication history</strong> — emails, calls, or messages you exchange with our admissions team.</li>
        <li><strong>Basic technical data</strong> — pages visited, device type, and approximate location, collected by GitHub Pages and any analytics we may add in future.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under the age of 18 without parental consent.</p>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To respond to your admissions or general inquiries.</li>
        <li>To send you information about our programs, application status, and campus events.</li>
        <li>To improve our website and the services we offer prospective students.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations under Indian law.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How Your Information Is Shared</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share inquiry data only with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Form delivery service</strong> — Web3Forms processes form submissions and delivers them to our admissions inbox.</li>
        <li><strong>Service providers</strong> — third parties who help us operate the website (e.g. GitHub Pages for hosting, Google Maps for the campus map embed).</li>
        <li><strong>Government authorities</strong> — when required by law, court order, or in response to a valid legal request.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain inquiry data only as long as necessary to respond to your request and to maintain our admissions records, after which it is deleted or anonymised.</p>

      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data when it is no longer needed.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for further communications.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:admission@stclaretcollegeofnursing.com">admission@stclaretcollegeofnursing.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>6. Cookies & Local Storage</h2>
      <p>Our website uses minimal browser storage — for example, a flag that prevents the admissions popup from re-appearing for 30 days after you submit or dismiss it. We do not use third-party advertising cookies.</p>

      <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Our website links to social media accounts (Instagram, YouTube) and embeds Google Maps. Those services have their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to review.</p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorised access. However, no method of internet transmission is fully secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top will reflect any changes. Continued use of the site after a revision constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        St. Claret College of Nursing<br />
        Veeraiah Nagar, Arasinakunte, Dasanapura,<br />
        Karnataka — 562162, India<br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:admission@stclaretcollegeofnursing.com">admission@stclaretcollegeofnursing.com</a><br />
        Phone: <a href="tel:+919847139798">+91 98471 39798</a>
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
